{"word":"H5801 - עִזָּבֹון - ʻizzâbôwn - iz-zaw-bone' - Fair","slug":"H5801","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">עִזָּבֹון</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʻizzâbôwn"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>iz-zaw-bone'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Fair"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E2;&#x05D6;&#x05BC;&#x05D1;&#x05D5;&#x05DF; - &#x201B;izza&#x0302;bo&#x0302;n</b> - <i>iz-zaw-bone'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H5800\">H5800</a> in the sense of <i>letting go</i> (for a price, that is, <i>selling</i>); <i>trade</i>, that is, the palce (<i>mart</i>) or the payment (<i>revenue</i>): - fair, ware."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H5800\">H5800</a>, <a href=\"#/H5805\">H5805</a>, <a href=\"#/H5806\">H5806</a>"}]}